rComments: One of the best professors at U of T - she is extremly well-versed in the study of religion and politics and where/how they intersect. Attendance was worth 10% and an extra 5% awarded for posting blogs to Blackboard. One TA from Religion and the other from Poli Sci, both were fair. Final research paper was workshopped for 2 hours in class.

A wonderful professor! One of the best I have ever had. Very inspirational and helpful as person. Lectures are super intellectually stimulating. She makes you read but the materials are interesting and it's worth the effort.
